TextBody:
Hello Lucas,

My name is Ramon with Netwrix Technical Support and I have been assigned to this case. Will you please answer the following questions to better assist you?

•        What is the impact of the issue on your business? 
•        Who is affected by this issue?
•        What are the steps to reproduce?
•        Have you attempted any troubleshooting steps yet? If so, what have you tried?
•        When did this issue start?
•        On what platform is your Endpoint Protector hosted? (on-prem, AWS, Google cloud platform, Azure, Hosted by EPP on AWS)
•        Screen shots, logs, other artifacts, etc.

Also, what day and times (please include time zone) would you be available to schedule a remote session for this issue?


Thank you.

Best Regards, 
Ramon Torres | Technical Support Engineer

- Created a new server and the costumer remade all policies and
configuration.
- Since its a new server, the old license cannot be applied to this one.
- Can you please generate a new license for this server: IWPDIRG0

Best regards,
